ges/kermit3.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 8/25 - Fear</span><hr size=1> Or, if your heavy agro casters want to keep casting, have them move into melee range of the mob before casting...That way, when the mob does agro, it moves no where.<br>
